#. Title = CHURCH / WATERBASINS
#. Description = Waterbasin dialogue for solving the "Move the waterbasins" task.
#. Actor = Water Bowls
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000570001CD1C"
msgid "It's awfully silent again, as if someone turned off the entire world outside those walls. Water inside the bowls stands still."
msgstr ""
"Le silence écrasant est de retour, comme si le monde entier s’était éteint à l’extérieur. Dans les bassines, aucune ride ne trouble la surface de l’eau."

#. Title = CHURCH / WATERBASINS
#. Description = Waterbasin dialogue for solving the "Move the waterbasins" task.
#. Actor = Soona, the Programmer
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000570001CD72"
msgid "The lead programmer sends you an encouraging thumbs up from across the hall."
msgstr ""
"La programmeuse en chef vous encourage en levant les pouces de l’autre côté du hall."

#. Title = CHURCH / WATERBASINS
#. Description = Waterbasin dialogue for solving the "Move the waterbasins" task.
#. Actor = Logic
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000570001CD7A"
msgid "This task is an insult to your mental skills."
msgstr ""
"C’est une insulte à ton intelligence."

#. Title = CHURCH / WATERBASINS
#. Description = Waterbasin dialogue for solving the "Move the waterbasins" task.
#. Actor = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000570001CD34"
msgid "Move the third bowl from the left two centimetres away."
msgstr ""
"Écarter la troisième bassine en partant de la gauche de 2 cm."

#. Title = CHURCH / WATERBASINS
#. Description = Waterbasin dialogue for solving the "Move the waterbasins" task.
#. Actor = Pain Threshold
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100002100002C25"
msgid "*And* your leg still hurts from the tribunal."
msgstr ""
"Et vous avez *accessoirement* toujours mal à la jambe depuis le tribunal."

#. Title = CHURCH / WATERBASINS
#. Description = Waterbasin dialogue for solving the "Move the waterbasins" task.
#. Actor = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000570001CD26"
msgid "Move the fourth bowl from the left five centimetres to the right."
msgstr ""
"Déplacer la quatrième bassine en partant de la gauche de 5 cm vers la droite."

#. Title = CHURCH / WATERBASINS
#. Description = Waterbasin dialogue for solving the "Move the waterbasins" task.
#. Actor = Perception (Sight)
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000570001CFAC"
msgid "Measurements have been marked down around the bowls, each chalk-drawn line representing a centimetre on the floor."
msgstr ""
"Autour des bassines, des mesures sont marquées sur le sol. Chaque trait de craie représente un centimètre."

#. Title = CHURCH / WATERBASINS
#. Description = Waterbasin dialogue for solving the "Move the waterbasins" task.
#. Actor = Water Bowls
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000570001CD40"
msgid "Some water spills out of the bowl, wetting the floor."
msgstr ""
"Un peu d’eau éclabousse le sol."

#. Title = CHURCH / WATERBASINS
#. Description = Waterbasin dialogue for solving the "Move the waterbasins" task.
#. Actor = Physical Instrument
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000021000028A7"
msgid "Time to run back! Or maybe walk, this *is* a sacred place after all..."
msgstr ""
"Allez, vas-y, cours jusqu’à elle ! Enfin marche, plutôt. C’est quand même un lieu sacré, ici."

#. Title = CHURCH / WATERBASINS
#. Description = Waterbasin dialogue for solving the "Move the waterbasins" task.
#. Actor = Water Bowls
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000570001CD3A"
msgid "It moves like a ghost without creating a single trace of sound."
msgstr ""
"Elle se déplace sans faire le moindre son, comme un fantôme."

#. Title = CHURCH / WATERBASINS
#. Description = Waterbasin dialogue for solving the "Move the waterbasins" task.
#. Actor = Interfacing
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000570001CD62"
msgid "Oh boy, this is going to be good."
msgstr ""
"Alors là, je sens qu’on va s’amuser."

#. Title = CHURCH / WATERBASINS
#. Description = Waterbasin dialogue for solving the "Move the waterbasins" task.
#. Actor = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000570001CD2C"
msgid "[Leave.]"
msgstr ""
"[Partir.]"
